metadata.name: Jay Greathouse-Panpsychic Animism
metadata.description:
Panpsychic Animism

Representing Hyposubjects within a technological Hyperobject. This animated GIF includes the individual PNG image “Tsukumogami Tulpa and Waifu” OE as one of the160 images in the animation.

Jay Greathouse Bio:

I make art in cognition and representation of our position as Hyposubjects within Hyperobjects in the context of Object-Oriented Ontology (OOO) and Speculative Realism.
